===2012-03-29 16:14 ===
*display_page():
===2012-03-29 16:14 ===
*Learning select: select * from flash_deck where status='Learning' and listno=1 and userno=1 
===2012-03-29 16:14 ===
*Wrong select: select * from flash_deck where status='Learning' and correct=0 and listno=1 and userno=1 
===2012-03-29 16:14 ===
*Unseen select: select * from flash_deck where status='Learning' and correct=0 and seen=0 and listno=1 and userno=1 
===2012-03-29 16:14 ===
*Display Card select: select flash_deck.cardno,name,image,value from flash_deck,flash_cards where cardid=cardno and  status='Learning' and correct=0 and seen=0 and flash_deck.listno=1 and flash_deck.userno=1  and flash_cards.listno=1 and flash_cards.userno=1 order by ordval limit 1

*Display Card select: select cardno, name,image from flash_deck,flash_cards where cardno=cardid and cardno=4 and flash_deck.listno=1 and flash_deck.userno=1 and flash_cards.listno=1 and flash_cards.userno=1

===2012-03-29 16:14 ===
*imageurl: tarot/04themperor.jpg
===2012-03-29 16:14 ===
*false cards: select cardid ,value, rand() as rnd from flash_cards where cardid<>4 and listno=1 and userno=1  order by rnd limit 4
===2012-03-29 16:14 ===
*display_flashdeck():
===2012-03-29 16:14 ===
*correctcards sel: select cardno from flash_deck where correct=1 and status='Learning'  and listno=1 and userno=1 
===2012-03-29 16:14 ===
*seencards sel: select cardno from flash_deck where seen=1 and status='Learning'  and listno=1 and userno=1 
===2012-03-29 16:14 ===
*cards sel: select flash_deck.cardno,name,correct,seen,value from flash_deck,flash_cards  where cardno=cardid and status='Learning' and flash_deck.listno=1 and flash_deck.userno=1  and flash_cards.listno=1 and flash_cards.userno=1    order by correct, seen , ordval
